<page>
   <topic>PAGE_COUNT Function</topic>
   <syntax>Result as N = page_count(C expr )</syntax>
   <arguments>
     <argument>
         <name>Result</name>
         <description>The number entries of a field on a report page.</description>
     </argument>
     <argument>
         <name>expr</name>
         <description>The fully qualified fieldname (i.e. tablename->fieldname )</description>
     </argument>
   </arguments>
   <description>Public user defined function.</description>
   <discussion>
PAGE_COUNT() counts the number entries of a field on a report page. This function can only be used on a report page.

   </discussion>
   <example><![CDATA[
? page_count("product->cost")
= 3

]]></example>
   
   <see>
      <ref>Report Functions and Methods</ref>
   </see>
 
</page>